10/01/2024
Erased Memories Anomaly Season - Details

From October to December, Agents can take part in the Erased Memories Anomaly Season, competing across multiple Events to earn the most Season Points for their Faction.

In addition, by taking part in some of these Events, Agents will be able to earn one or more of the Erased Memories Agent Profile medals.

In Erased Memories, a final set of world-changing events lie in the hands of Agents, and the outcome of the Anomaly series will change one universe’s past, present and future.

In a Cryptic universe, a driven and dynamic scientist discovered a way to achieve her destiny. She will ensure the future of her world is Enlightened.

An artifact, Buried deep by an ancient clan of Enlightened mystics, will play a vital role.

Memories, Shared across dimensions, unite a group that stands to understand, and perhaps oppose, her plan.

Their fate, and the actions of Agents around the world, will determine whether it is possible to Erase a part of reality in a way that has never been attempted before.

