Erased Memories Anomaly Season Scoring
The final outcome of the Erased Memories Anomaly Season will be based on the total Season Score accrued by each Faction from all of the above components, and the Faction with the higher final score will claim the Season.

For more details about how each component will contribute to the Season Score, see the associated sections for each component below.

